This is Path Raiders — a Phaser 3 TypeScript strategy game (web + mobile).

Engine: Phaser 3.
Language: TypeScript.
Bundler: Vite.
Backend: Supabase.
Factions: machines | plants | wizards.

Game world: 2560x720px.
Two horizontal lanes: Lane1 y=200, Lane2 y=520.
Left base = Player 1 (host), attacks right.
Right base = P2 (guest), attacks left.

Unit tokens are 64x64px silhouette PNGs from public/assets/tokens/
Spritesheets: 960x96px horizontal strip, 10 frames (idle_0-3, walk_0-5).

Supabase client always imported from src/lib/supabase.ts
gameState singleton always imported from src/lib/gameState.ts

Always use Phaser scene events for cross-scene communication.
GSD planning files are in .planning/ — reference them for context.
